<span class="comment"><font color=#000000>&#62; Look at that in comparison with all the hatred and anger around here directed at the record companies and you can see why I find it so disturbing.<p>I wonder how much of that is from media influencing society, which in turn influences media, looping it back around.  Compare US media where almost all bad guys suffer and die painfully to those of some other countries, where few people are wholly evil and decent people are able to come to an understanding in the end, after fighting out their differences.</font></span><p><font size=1><u><a href="reply?id=3493166&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%57%36%4a%67%72%54%34%55%43%6b">reply</a></u></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=240></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_3497220 href="vote?for=3497220&dir=up&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%57%36%4a%67%72%54%34%55%43%6b"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_3497220></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=rdl">rdl</a> 12 days ago  | <a href="item?id=3497220">link</a></span></div><br>
